text:
Breaking Barriers in the Trades
From surviving head-on collisions to mentoring female engineers against company resistance - the true impact of blue collar mentorship can change careers and lives. When leadership means creating space for talent regardless of gender. #Tradesman #Craftsmanship #Plumber #Electrician #Carpenter #Welder #Mechanic #ConstructionLife #HVACTech #Masonry #Pipefitter #SheetMetal #Roofer #Painter #AutoTech #Handyman

The Human Pipe Snake: Construction’s Most Valuable Asset
